Goodnight Moon. Write an alt ending, the narrator of the story is arrested
text:
In the style of the book good night moon, write an alternative ending where the narrator of the story is arrested for reading to children of strangers

Good night stars, Good night air, Good night noises everywhere.

Good night police, Good night jail, Good night to the storyteller, who must now tell her tale.

Good night officers, Good night cell, Good night to the tale-teller, who must now bid farewell.

Good night law, Good night judge, Good night to the storyteller, now in her new grudge.

Good night laws, Good night court, Good night to the storyteller, her freedom cut short.
